### ============================
### VERSION STATUSES
### ============================
### Izveido statusu "Sagatavē"
POST http://localhost:8080/api/version-statuses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sagatavē",
  "description": "Versija tiek izstrādāta"
}

###

### Izveido statusu "Apstiprināta"
POST http://localhost:8080/api/version-statuses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Apstiprināta",
  "description": "Versija apstiprināta ITF domē"
}

### Iegūst visus kursa versiju statusus
GET http://localhost:8080/api/version-statuses
Accept: application/json

###

### Atjauno statusa aprakstu (piemēram, id = 1)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/version-statuses/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Izstrādē",
  "description": "Versija joprojām tiek papildināta"
}

###

### Dzēš statusu pēc ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/version-statuses/2

