### ============================
### COURSE VERSIONS
### ============================

### Izveidot jaunu kursa versiju (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/course-versions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "versionNumber": 2,
  "slug": "java-v2",
  "isArchived": false,
  "isActive": false,
  "approvalDate": "2025-05-11",
  "decisionNumber": "Nr. 25-03",
  "decisionReference": "ITF dome, 2025. gada 10. maijs",
  "course": {
    "id": "5a26d81f-210b-47d6-8ff0-0f113d219b7b"
  },
  "status": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "academicYear": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "semester": {
    "id": 1
  }
}

###

### Iegūst visas kursa versijas
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-versions
Accept: application/json

###

### Iegūst visas versijas konkrētam kursam
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-versions/by-course/5a26d81f-210b-47d6-8ff0-0f113d219b7b
Accept: application/json

###

### Iegūst konkrētu kursa versiju pēc ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-versions/81cd8cd1-bd7b-4182-a2be-e00d22290692
Accept: application/json

###

### Dzēš kursa versiju pēc ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/course-versions/81cd8cd1-bd7b-4182-a2be-e00d22290692